Foreign Exchange

Are you looking for competitive rates for your foreign currency transactions? Then UBA Ghana is your right partner. We are very active in Foreign Exchange transactions and we guarantee the following:

  • Flexible & well Structured deals
  • Timely, comprehensive and assured delivery
  • Competitive rates
  • Highly skilled experts who provide you with special advisory services
